<varlistentry id="options.SideBevel">
	<term>SideBevel <emphasis remap='I'>Bottom|Extra|NoInline|NoOutline|none|Left|Right|Top</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Sets the default bevel of a window s frame sides.</para>
		<para>If you need different bevels for the different window states, use SideFocusedBevel, SideUnfocusedBevel, SideStickyBevel</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Bevel#synopsis">Bevel flags</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>


